(2, '124 Âu Cơ', '124 Au Co Street', '21.062995, 105.832164', 'http://duanoceangatenhatrang.com/glocalhome/assets/img/header-bg.jpg', '124-au-co', '#', 'We now have two rooms available on the 3rd floor. Both are 15 sqm, sharing a bathroom. Room 302 has a balcony while room 301’s inside is a bit bigger, but still have a large window.\r\nRoom 302 has the all essentials like bed (along with mattress, bedding), wardrobe, air conditioner. You could move in right away if necessary, or request further furnishing of your choice.\r\nRoom 301 has the same furniture, plus a makeup table and more storage space.\r\nFor other areas, you can get all the features a shared house supposed to have: spacious parking and with cozy living room on the 1st floor, a kitchen dining area with lot’s of cooking tools on the 2nd, (TV and fridge will be included) and the rooftop area where you could do the laundry and relax.\r\nThere are Vinmart and local markets, cafes nearby. You can access the house from two directions in case of bad traffic. The only downside is that one entry''s first section is a bit bumpy.\r\nWe are residing on the 4th floor, and can''t wait for you to join us!\r\n', '2017-09-27 07:53:39'),
