(1423, '88 Tô Ngọc Vân', '88 To Ngoc Van', '21.0681693,105.82267550000006', '', '88-to-ngoc-van', '#', 'We currently have two 21sqm-rooms (on the 2nd and 3rd floor) with bathroom ensuite available. They’re Ideal for guests who need to move in as soon as possible. \r\n\r\nThis place previously attracted a lot of artists, since there is an art gallery/ small cafe on the first floor, where you could relax and enjoy both the artworks and drinks.\r\n\r\nThe location is usually quiet, yet filled with places for various activities beside restaurants and cafes, such as art learning center, coworking spaces, swimming pool and gym… just a few steps away.\r\n\r\nThe rooms are partially furnished with bed, wardrobe, air conditioner, fridge, bathroom equipments \r\nGuests can order to install private kitchen or more furniture supplies from us that suits your needs.\r\nOtherwise, early-booking guests can receive discount if you can bring your furniture over and/or use the shared kitchen on the 4th floor. You could also do your laundry in this floor.\r\n', '2017-10-26 23:41:23');
